00Z","msg":"#法律知識<br />\n<br />\n警方可以根據警隊條例54(1)對任何行動可疑的人，或54(2)對任何有合理懷疑已犯法的人進行截查。<br />\n<br />\n若你被無理截查，本頻道建議直接引用法律條文質問警方：<br />\n✅根據哪一條警隊條例進行截查；<br />\n✅如果回答54(1)，可追問警方為何你行動可疑；<br />\n✅如果回答54(2)，請追問警方為何懷疑你已經或準備犯法。<br />\n<br />\n案例指出警方應根據客觀事實（時間、地點、現場情況、行為等）作主觀判斷。<br />\n<br />\n‼️截查期間，警方不能要求你解鎖或關閉手機。"},{"pid":"e6e5245585f74e8ef03fc44dab926e77e27e66ad","tid":1602580,"uid":249022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc21179f18ad9d8950303bbc0d6452b38bf1f0aa","tid":1602580,"uid":56721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"係我就噴D入佢油箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:19:46.000Z","msg":"擺幾粒方糖入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cebf8faaf59b3fa81b74db45cb477a51cc8a7f","tid":1602580,"uid":117225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc21179f18ad9d8950303bbc0d6452b38bf1f0aa","tid":1602580,"uid":56721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"係我就噴D入佢油箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"石油氣箱唔好亂開<br />\n（真心識先好玩"},{"pid":"3c4c0126238eeca380f398b7fd6ffd340f945b61","tid":1602580,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:55:56.000Z","msg":"個的士佬冇穿冇爛 香港人真係威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b83d45831786c6be1dd3ce78bc2bd494a062fa","tid":1602580,"uid":101507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T22:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pofPABP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpofPABP.jpg&h=fdb9a8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCsna99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih